                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171203-144-off777 t18171203-144-cd778"></join>, 70lbs. of lead, value 20s., belonging to 
                     
                        <persName id="t18171203-144-victim1065" type="victimName">
